videos.headline: Evans picks up his 2nd TD of the game
videos.description: Darrynton Evans runs eight yards into the end zone to pad Appalachian State's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Evans picks up his 2nd TD of the game) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Evans scores 3rd TD of 1st quarter
videos.description: Darrynton Evans catches a short pass and shakes off a tackler to get into the end zone for a five-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Evans scores 3rd TD of 1st quarter) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Lewis, Leblanc connect to get Louisiana on the board
videos.description: Levi Lewis goes deep to Peter Leblanc, who brushes off a defender and gets into the end zone for a 37-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Lewis, Leblanc connect to get Louisiana on the board) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Williams takes it home for 29-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Williams Jr. breaks through defenders for a 29-yard touchdown, giving Appalachian State a 28-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Williams takes it home for 29-yard TD) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Mitchell catches his 1st TD pass of the season for Louisiana
videos.description: Elijah Mitchell picks up his first touchdown catch of the season off a 1-yard pass from Levi Lewis.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Mitchell catches his 1st TD pass of the season for Louisiana) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Harrington gives Appalachian State its 5th TD of the 1st half
videos.description: Daetrich Harrington bursts through the middle and adds to Appalachian State's lead with a 25-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Harrington gives Appalachian State its 5th TD of the 1st half) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Thomas comes up with pick-six for Appalachian State
videos.description: Josh Thomas intercepts the ball on Levi Lewis' pass and runs it into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thomas comes up with pick-six for Appalachian State) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Lewis finds Bradley for short TD
videos.description: Levi Lewis throws to Ja'Marcus Bradley, who makes the catch for a 2-yard Louisiana touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Lewis finds Bradley for short TD) 2019/12/07
